***********************************************************************         
* ROUTINE TO FORMAT OCNEL DATA ITEMS AND APPEND USER-ID               *         
***********************************************************************         
         SPACE 1                                                                
FGETUID  BAS   RE,FMTCHRS                                                       
         SR    RF,RF                                                            
         IC    RF,FMTDATAL                                                      
         BCTR  RF,0                                                             
         MVC   TRWORK,FMTOUT       SWAP OUT DATA ITEM                           
         EX    RF,*-6                                                           
         MVC   FMTOUT(0),BLANKS    AND CLEAR                                    
         EX    RF,*-6                                                           
*                                  INSERT USER-ID                               
         BAS   RE,DISPID           DISPLAY ID                                   
*                                                                               
         L     R3,FULL             RESTORE PRINT LOCATION                       
         SR    RF,RF                                                            
         IC    RF,FMTDATAL                                                      
         BCTR  RF,0                                                             
         MVC   2(0,R3),TRWORK      REPLACE DATA ITEM                            
